Look, I'm not who you think. Please.

680
01:04:30,160 --> 01:04:33,835
All right, all right, avoid the fate
of your late beloved boyfriend.

681
01:04:50,520 --> 01:04:52,476
Was he your pimp?

682
01:04:52,600 --> 01:04:54,556
What?

683
