You know, Gar, between you and me,

702
01:06:15,680 --> 01:06:18,513
what do you really know about Roberta?

703
01:06:18,920 --> 01:06:20,876
Nice wallpaper.

704
01:06:36,960 --> 01:06:39,633
Don't you think
you ought to wait for Roberta

705
01:06:39,760 --> 01:06:41,751
